**Image Generation Prompt (EN)**

A sun-drenched tropical garden courtyard in a historic sandstone building in a small German town. Late afternoon golden light filters through wide banana and palm leaves onto colorful mismatched wooden tables and chairs. A still ornamental pond reflects green foliage. Handmade ceramic mugs and a deep-red rum punch in a curved glass sit on a weathered wooden table. Warm string lights begin to glow in the background. Lush strelitzia plants frame the scene. The atmosphere is relaxed, intimate, unhurried — like a private garden in the Caribbean transported to a Franconian courtyard. Real, lived-in feel: no stock-photo perfection, slight imperfections welcome. Color palette: deep tropical greens, terracotta, warm amber, coral accents. No people, focus on place and mood. Aspect ratio 16:9, photorealistic, shallow depth of field, golden-hour warmth.

